# Session detail: per-model + subagent breakdown with resume command
Output tools/vhs/.render.gif

Set Shell zsh
Set FontSize 14
Set Width 1440
Set Height 660
Set Padding 20

Hide
Type "sh tools/vhs/.demo/run.sh"
Enter
Sleep 9s
Type "3"
Sleep 1s
Enter
Sleep 1s
Show
Sleep 2s
Screenshot assets/detail.png
Sleep 1s
